{"type": "article", "id": 4132, "title": "创意冰格", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-05T08:25:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 17, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233058QX6b0VOGFA7Iq3J2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t喜欢喝冰酒、冻奶茶、冰可乐的人不在少数，但却总是因为冰块的融化而影响了饮品本身的味道，就拿酒来说吧，酒味减淡总是件扫兴的事。这款名叫「Whiskey Wedge」的创意冰格估计能满足好酒之人，用户只需将它放入酒杯，然后灌入水，水将依冰格的形状冷冻凝结位一个斜坡状的冰块，而且能与酒隔开，有效保证酒的原始味道，亦能享受冰镇的口感。定价 14.95 美元，<a href=\"http://www.uncommongoods.com/product/whiskey-wedge\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233057N0ZO35YqCm4jk6iT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330589iUpAxgGRoCFm6nh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}